{"act_version":"0.1","id":"api/buckets/create","type":"reference","title":"Create a bucket","summary":"Provision a new storage bucket in the workspace.","summary_source":"author","content":[{"type":"prose","format":"markdown","text":"## Request"},{"type":"code","language":"bash","text":"curl -X POST -H 'Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN' \\\n  -d '{\"name\":\"my-bucket\",\"region\":\"us-east-1\"}' \\\n  https://api.tinybox.dev/v1/buckets"},{"type":"prose","format":"markdown","text":"## Response\n\nThe API returns the created bucket descriptor. See [List buckets](/docs/api/buckets/list)."}],"tokens":{"summary":8,"body":28},"metadata":{"source":{"adapter":"act-docusaurus-sidebar-synthesizer","source_id":"api/buckets/create.md","source_path":"api/buckets/create.md"}},"etag":"s256:bqm1SXDv7AZcusab05HxCI","related":[{"id":"api/buckets/list","relation":"see-also"},{"id":"api/buckets/delete","relation":"see-also"}],"source":{"human_url":"https://example.com/api/buckets/create/"},"parent":"buckets"}